data.text:
Bangkok, Thailand - January, 1974 : At Don Mueang Air Force Airport, Dr.Sanya Thammasak, Prime Minister, and Phanga Thammasak, his wife, as well as the farewell group to Mr. Kakuei Tanaka, Prime Minister of Japan, and daughter. At the plane door, Kakuei Tanaka and his daughter waved goodbye to Thailand's Prime Minister and his delegation.
